column3: Used as a separator between component data elements contained within a composite data element (default value: ":")
Used to separate two simple or composite data elements (default value: "+")
Used to indicate the character used for decimal notation (default value: ".")
Used to restore any service character to its original specification (default value: "?")
Used to indicate the character used for repetition separation (default value: "*")
Used to indicate the end of segment data (default value: "'")
